Problem 6
Which schools in Community Areas 10 to 15 are healthy school certified?

%sql SELECT NAME_OF_SCHOOL \
FROM CHICAGO_PUBLIC_SCHOOLS \
WHERE COMMUNITY_AREA_NUMBER BETWEEN 10 AND 15 \
AND HEALTHY_SCHOOL_CERTIFIED = 'Yes'

